         <head>Transliteration Principles</head>
         <p>For any questions regarding transliteration that should arise after
         reading the guidelines, individual issues should be opened.</p>
         <p>You can use
         <ref target="https://betamasaheft.github.io/transliteration/">this
         tool</ref> to update text transcribed according to the old convention
         to these or to enter fidal or correctly transcribed text and get the
         other of the two.</p>
